<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="49000000t" end="65000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">我是对的</p>
<p begin="72700000t" end="82700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">火怜…</p>
<p begin="83900000t" end="105900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">总之先告诉我们发生了什么吧</p>
<p begin="110200000t" end="144000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">你不是要让我听听你的猛将传吗</p>
<p begin="147200000t" end="154200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">哼</p>
<p begin="155300000t" end="176800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">我再说一遍  大号的妹妹</p>
<p begin="179900000t" end="193700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">告诉我发生了什么</p>
<p begin="194500000t" end="216400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">我  才  不  说  呢</p>
<p begin="241800000t" end="252500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">阿良良木君</p>
<p begin="266000000t" end="318900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">记得阿良良木君在我被爸爸打的时候很生气对吧</p>
<p begin="326500000t" end="365600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">而那个阿良良木君又为什么想要打火怜妹妹呢</p>
<p begin="379000000t" end="416600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">我觉得体罚有时也是必需的</p>
<p begin="419800000t" end="435600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">如果阿良良木君能够好好地说出一个</p>
<p begin="436900000t" end="480800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">能让挨打的火怜妹妹服气的理由</p>
<p begin="484400000t" end="503700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">那倒无所谓</p>
<p begin="507000000t" end="517700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">对不起</p>
<p begin="520400000t" end="538300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">为什么要向我道歉呢</p>
<p begin="541200000t" end="565000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">抱歉  我太激动了</p>
<p begin="566200000t" end="593400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">翼姐姐  请不要责怪哥哥</p>
<p begin="600500000t" end="618900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">刚才都是我不好</p>
<p begin="621600000t" end="655800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">而且如果被打的话  我一定会还击的</p>
<p begin="657600000t" end="685200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">是吗  那看来是我多管闲事了吗</p>
<p begin="687400000t" end="700500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">就是啊  翼姐姐</p>
<p begin="703000000t" end="737700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">但是我不觉得火怜妹妹能还得了手</p>
<p begin="739300000t" end="757900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">就算还不了手也能以牙还牙</p>
<p begin="760600000t" end="788400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">翼姐姐你不知道我的牙有多硬</p>
<p begin="799100000t" end="824000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">哥哥  请心平气和地听我说</p>
<p begin="832900000t" end="876100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">这次Fire Sisters稍微请羽川姐姐帮了点忙</p>
<p begin="877300000t" end="887900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">这你叫我怎么心平气和！</p>
<p begin="889200000t" end="897900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">阿良良木君</p>
<p begin="901200000t" end="919800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">不要发出太大的声音</p>
<p begin="922900000t" end="938900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">会把你父母吵醒的</p>
<p begin="941800000t" end="987800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">而且原来阿良良木君会像这样朝妹妹怒吼来恐吓她们吗</p>
<p begin="990000000t" end="999100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">真让人意外</p>
<p begin="1006000000t" end="1017100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">（想在羽川面前装乖）</p>
<p begin="1006300000t" end="1015400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">真难做到！</p>
<p begin="1019700000t" end="1051000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">羽川姐姐  请不要责怪哥哥</p>
<p begin="1055000000t" end="1107800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">哥哥只是在担心我们有没有给姐姐你添麻烦</p>
<p begin="1111200000t" end="1118400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">真是的…</p>
<p begin="1121400000t" end="1169600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">阿良良木君  我是自愿协助火怜和月火妹妹的</p>
<p begin="1173800000t" end="1194300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">要怪她们的话就怪错人了</p>
<p begin="1198400000t" end="1215300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">我所认识的阿良良木君</p>
<p begin="1218200000t" end="1248700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">可不是个会拿妹妹出气的人对吧</p>
<p begin="1253100000t" end="1261800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">呜…</p>
<p begin="1268200000t" end="1276000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">嘿嘿</p>
<p begin="1277600000t" end="1289900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">好吧好吧</p>
<p begin="1292200000t" end="1310390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">我答应你们不生气</p>
<p begin="1312300000t" end="1331200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">也对爸爸和妈妈保密？</p>
<p begin="1333100000t" end="1363200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">当然  所以快点向我说明</p>
<p begin="1365300000t" end="1383000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">究竟发生了什么事情</p>
<p begin="1384900000t" end="1409900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">那么  究竟发生了什么事情呢</p>
<p begin="1431500000t" end="1458000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">羽川  可以到我的房间来一下吗</p>
<p begin="1459500000t" end="1486500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">哥哥想要把翼姐姐骗进自己的房间啊</p>
<p begin="1490200000t" end="1500200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">（总有一天要宰了你）</p>
<p begin="1502900000t" end="1515500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">好啊  走吧</p>
<p begin="1529000000t" end="1554400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">放心吧  火怜妹妹  月火妹妹</p>
<p begin="1558300000t" end="1579400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">因为你们所做的事情是正确的</p>
<p begin="1581000000t" end="1616800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">只要听了我的话  阿良良木君也一定会明白的</p>
<p begin="1619000000t" end="1639400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">我会好好解释的  请不要担心</p>
<p begin="1640700000t" end="1652600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">羽川姐姐…</p>
<p begin="1640700000t" end="1652600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">翼姐姐…</p>
<p begin="1678900000t" end="1718200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">因为我很信任你们这位哥哥啊</p>
<p begin="1757400000t" end="1773200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">喂  那边的大号的</p>
<p begin="1775200000t" end="1789300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">干嘛啊  小号的</p>
<p begin="1793200000t" end="1811900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">你确实没有错</p>
<p begin="1814700000t" end="1843000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">你总是正确的  这我可以肯定</p>
<p begin="1847900000t" end="1892100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">但也只是正确而已  你并不强大</p>
<p begin="1898300000t" end="1916600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">不够强大的家伙是会输的</p>
<p begin="1920400000t" end="1948900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">练习格斗技的你应该很清楚吧</p>
<p begin="1953900000t" end="1982100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">贯彻正义最重要的条件不是正确</p>
<p begin="1986500000t" end="1996800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">而是强大</p>
<p begin="2001600000t" end="2020900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">所以正义总会取得胜利</p>
<p begin="2025400000t" end="2045700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">你差不多也给我意识到这点吧</p>
<p begin="2049300000t" end="2064000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">只要没弄明白这点</p>
<p begin="2066500000t" end="2088800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">你们的所作所为就永远只是</p>
<p begin="2093000000t" end="2111400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">扮演正义伙伴的游戏</p>
<p begin="2112900000t" end="2122100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">也就是冒牌货</p>
<p begin="2112900000t" end="2122100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">伪物</p>
<p begin="2354300000t" end="2392300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">今朝目が覚めたら　忘れちゃった</p>
<p begin="2354300000t" end="2392300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">今早睁开眼睛　差点忘了</p>
<p begin="2403100000t" end="2464400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">夢の続き　まだあたし待っていた</p>
<p begin="2403100000t" end="2464400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">昨天的梦　依然在等我去延续</p>
<p begin="2465500000t" end="2502600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">運命だよこれ　ほっとけない</p>
<p begin="2465500000t" end="2502600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">这就是命运　不能置之不理</p>
<p begin="2511600000t" end="2568800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">理由があるんだ　正義の味方だから</p>
<p begin="2511600000t" end="2568800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">我可是有理由的　因为我是正义的伙伴</p>
<p begin="2575290000t" end="2681400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">燃えるこの温度に　溶けるその答えは</p>
<p begin="2575290000t" end="2681400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">融化于炙热的温度中　这份答案就是</p>
<p begin="2684100000t" end="2754300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">清く正しくそして格好良く</p>
<p begin="2684100000t" end="2754300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">光明磊落　正直善良　帅气无比</p>
<p begin="2756000000t" end="2784700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">なくちゃね</p>
<p begin="2756000000t" end="2784700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">就这么简单</p>
<p begin="2786100000t" end="2838800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">手をつなぎ　どこまでも行こう</p>
<p begin="2786100000t" end="2838800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">牵起双手　勇往直前吧</p>
<p begin="2841100000t" end="2893700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">頭より先に早く</p>
<p begin="2841100000t" end="2893700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">别想那么多</p>
<p begin="2895000000t" end="2946800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">君となら　どこまでも行ける</p>
<p begin="2895000000t" end="2946800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">和你一起　世界任我行</p>
<p begin="2949700000t" end="3006000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">きっと　ずっと　もっと</p>
<p begin="2949700000t" end="3006000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">一定能　始终　更进一步</p>
<p begin="2990000000t" end="3090000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">本字幕仅供交流试看之用，如你喜欢本作品，请支持购买正版。</p>
<p begin="2990000000t" end="3090000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">翻译、校对：痛爱的飞鱼、酱小鱼、detectivexsc、老伯；</p>
<p begin="3090100000t" end="3114100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">要比较阿良良木姐妹——Fire Sisters两人的话</p>
<p begin="3090100000t" end="3114100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">火怜和月火还是小学生的时候——当然我那时也是小学生了</p>
<p begin="3090100000t" end="3114100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">为了救助因某种原因被某些东西逼到绝境的火怜</p>
<p begin="3090100000t" end="3114100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">总之</p>
<p begin="3090100000t" end="3114100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">有意图的暴走</p>
<p begin="3094800000t" end="3119800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">火怜与蜜蜂  其四</p>
<p begin="3141500000t" end="3153300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">感觉真新鲜啊</p>
<p begin="3154400000t" end="3159700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">啊？</p>
<p begin="3160800000t" end="3190700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">我是指  阿良良木君对待妹妹的担心方式</p>
<p begin="3193500000t" end="3277400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">与对待我  战场原同学  真宵妹妹  神原同学和千石妹妹时完全不一样</p>
<p begin="3279800000t" end="3313900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">怎么说才好呢  感觉似乎更加拼命呢</p>
<p begin="3316200000t" end="3328300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">拼命什么的…</p>
<p begin="3329500000t" end="3365400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">阿良良木君在对待妹妹时用的是另一个人格呢</p>
<p begin="3379700000t" end="3407200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">你刚才说的还真是严厉呢</p>
<p begin="3412200000t" end="3432900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">虽然正确但不够强大？</p>
<p begin="3436900000t" end="3469800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">听起来就像是你在说自己一样</p>
<p begin="3474300000t" end="3495600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">你想说这是同属厌恶吗</p>
<p begin="3497700000t" end="3515500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">你是不想被人这么说吧</p>
<p begin="3521400000t" end="3579300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">不过  硬要说的不是同属厌恶反而是自我厌恶吧</p>
<p begin="3582300000t" end="3647900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">羽川  你和她们认识也才不过一个月  所以可能还不清楚</p>
<p begin="3651800000t" end="3702800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">我和火怜妹妹一起生活了15年  和月火妹妹一起生活了近14年</p>
<p begin="3707000000t" end="3726300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">以我的经验来说…</p>
<p begin="3727900000t" end="3741600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">噗…呵呵</p>
<p begin="3742700000t" end="3755200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">羽…羽川？</p>
<p begin="3757700000t" end="3775200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">啊…抱歉抱歉</p>
<p begin="3777700000t" end="3822300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">不过阿良良木君在称呼妹妹们时也加上「妹妹」呢</p>
<p begin="3823900000t" end="3829100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">什…</p>
<p begin="3830300000t" end="3839900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">究极失误！</p>
<p begin="3865500000t" end="3879700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">不用在意的</p>
<p begin="3882200000t" end="3917100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">你看  我不也叫她们「火怜妹妹」  「月火妹妹」的嘛</p>
<p begin="3917900000t" end="3927400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">不  不是的</p>
<p begin="3929900000t" end="3960100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">刚才那个是…我只是在模仿羽川而已</p>
<p begin="3963900000t" end="3992000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">对了  是在修辞学上把她们视为孩子的表现手法</p>
<p begin="3994200000t" end="4007100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">我平时对她们都直呼其名的…</p>
<p begin="4035500000t" end="4055500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">总…总之  这些就暂且别管了</p>
<p begin="4062900000t" end="4106300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">进入正题吧  羽川  现在情况非常紧急</p>
<p begin="4110500000t" end="4125800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">是啊</p>
<p begin="4137700000t" end="4172800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">话说回来  枕头的部分我还是知道的</p>
<p begin="4176600000t" end="4223900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">她们好像是在寻找中学生间流传的诅咒的出处是吧</p>
<p begin="4227300000t" end="4246700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">哎  你为什么会知道</p>
<p begin="4249100000t" end="4263700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">实际上千石告诉了我</p>
<p begin="4267600000t" end="4285400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">虽然不是本意  但我家的妹妹们…</p>
<p begin="4286600000t" end="4302300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">火怜妹妹和月火妹妹</p>
<p begin="4315000000t" end="4325800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">我家的妹妹…</p>
<p begin="4326900000t" end="4343200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">火怜妹妹和月火妹妹～</p>
<p begin="4366700000t" end="4407300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">火怜妹妹和月火妹妹在中学生里非常有名</p>
<p begin="4411300000t" end="4444600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">千石好像也听说过她们的动向</p>
<p begin="4456500000t" end="4465500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">原来如此</p>
<p begin="4467600000t" end="4521100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">对了  这么说来千石妹妹本身以前也是那些诅咒的被害人吧</p>
<p begin="4522100000t" end="4541800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">正确来说是唯一的被害人吧</p>
<p begin="4544500000t" end="4581900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">不是唯一的  虽然说是最大的受害人</p>
<p begin="4581200000t" end="4588600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">「给我坐到床上去」</p>
<p begin="4586300000t" end="4631900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">因为诅咒在中学生之间产生了很多坏影响</p>
<p begin="4588600000t" end="4600000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">往床上劝比较好」</p>
<p begin="4600000000t" end="4610000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">千石就让我上床来着</p>
<p begin="4610000000t" end="4620000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">我一边回忆一边坐上椅子</p>
<p begin="4620000000t" end="4629000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">没错</p>
<p begin="4629000000t" end="4640000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">羽川翼穿的是制服</p>
<p begin="4633300000t" end="4641900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">各种各样是指？</p>
<p begin="4640000000t" end="4650000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">难道你没有私服吗？</p>
<p begin="4643900000t" end="4666600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">基本上是人际关系的恶化</p>
<p begin="4650000000t" end="4659000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">「我有睡衣啊  你不是看过的吗」</p>
<p begin="4659000000t" end="4669000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">顺便一提  穿内衣的样子我也看过</p>
<p begin="4669000000t" end="4680400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">归根结底还是羽川以自己的眼光挑选的外出用服装啊</p>
<p begin="4675700000t" end="4719700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">根据我的调查  流行的诅咒基本以恶意的诅咒为主</p>
<p begin="4680400000t" end="4692000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">到底什么时候才能看到啊！</p>
<p begin="4692000000t" end="4703800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">就这么直接过来了  我是不是应该从那里</p>
<p begin="4703800000t" end="4720200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">「嗯  拜托了」</p>
<p begin="4727000000t" end="4745100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">偏向性非常明显</p>
<p begin="4748000000t" end="4826900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">她们两人认为有人故意而为之的推测  虽说基本上是胡乱猜测的</p>
<p begin="4830100000t" end="4860500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">但是也不是完全错误的</p>
<p begin="4871900000t" end="4906500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">顺便问一句  你是什么时候开始和她们共同行动的</p>
<p begin="4909900000t" end="4934400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">说不上是共同行动</p>
<p begin="4936100000t" end="4964700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">只是偶尔被拜托时帮帮她们而已</p>
<p begin="4970700000t" end="4995200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">硬要我回答是从什么时候开始的话…</p>
<p begin="4998900000t" end="5029900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">对呢  是暑假开始的时候吧</p>
<p begin="5043600000t" end="5067100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">那么  原来是你帮她们的啊</p>
<p begin="5069200000t" end="5093400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">也就是说已经查明犯人的身份了吧</p>
<p begin="5100600000t" end="5156100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">总之  当时打电话给火怜的不是别人  正是羽川翼</p>
<p begin="5163600000t" end="5192890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">你说成是我的错  这真是让人困扰啊</p>
<p begin="5194500000t" end="5233200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">忍野那家伙就是在警戒着你这种地方啊</p>
<p begin="5237100000t" end="5265100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">才能过于出众  绝对能够找到答案的地方</p>
<p begin="5268000000t" end="5311500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">是啊  但是我也不能因此而放手不管</p>
<p begin="5313700000t" end="5350900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">没错  就算我和火怜妹妹  月火妹妹…</p>
<p begin="5372400000t" end="5421200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">就像我和火怜妹妹  月火妹妹必须接受自己的弱小一样</p>
<p begin="5425200000t" end="5455900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">你也必须接受自己的强大</p>
<p begin="5465200000t" end="5506800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">于是  火怜妹妹去和查明的犯人直接谈判…</p>
<p begin="5510900000t" end="5525400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">然后被怎么样了吗？</p>
<p begin="5527900000t" end="5580600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">没错  我和她们分头行动  事后才被叫去现场的</p>
<p begin="5582600000t" end="5611200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">所以没有直接见到那个犯人</p>
<p begin="5614100000t" end="5672700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">至少在火怜妹妹见到犯人之前和她汇合的话  我或许还能有些办法</p>
<p begin="5676200000t" end="5707500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">火怜妹妹是怎么形容那个犯人的</p>
<p begin="5708900000t" end="5747700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">那个  好像是一个叫作「贝木泥舟」的…</p>
<p begin="5752700000t" end="5768300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">不吉的家伙</p>
<p begin="5811800000t" end="5861600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">照顾妹妹的任务暂时交给了羽川  我先去洗澡了</p>
<p begin="5868800000t" end="5890000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">如果不稍微花点时间冷静一下的话</p>
<p begin="5893500000t" end="5927000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">我估计又会对火怜和月火大吼大叫了</p>
<p begin="5948600000t" end="5962500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">对了  羽川</p>
<p begin="5964900000t" end="5970800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">嗯？</p>
<p begin="5972400000t" end="6002600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">你打电话给战场原时说了些什么</p>
<p begin="6004600000t" end="6016600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">啊  那个？</p>
<p begin="6020600000t" end="6074400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">月火用手机发消息给你后  说没马上回复很奇怪</p>
<p begin="6077000000t" end="6099800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">于是我就打电话过来了</p>
<p begin="6115000000t" end="6154200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">无论怎么说  那两个孩子还是很信赖「哥哥」的呢</p>
<p begin="6155100000t" end="6193500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">那个  我也知道姑且是这么个情况</p>
<p begin="6197600000t" end="6233100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">但是  你是怎么把战场原说服的</p>
<p begin="6235200000t" end="6242400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">没怎么样</p>
<p begin="6245800000t" end="6282100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">只是我听了战场原同学的声音后就了解了大致情况</p>
<p begin="6284300000t" end="6302600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">便简单地拜托她了</p>
<p begin="6304900000t" end="6320300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">简单地拜托？</p>
<p begin="6322700000t" end="6372100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">就说「你如果不讲道理的话  我就要对阿良良木君告白了哟」</p>
<p begin="6413900000t" end="6424100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">好可怕…</p>
<p begin="6589200000t" end="6596700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">请问…</p>
<p begin="6608100000t" end="6633500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">既然像这样看到了我的裸体</p>
<p begin="6635500000t" end="6677400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">也就是说你不得不娶我过门对吗</p>
<p begin="6679200000t" end="6694800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">我的主人</p>
<p begin="6697600000t" end="6712900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">小…小忍？</p>
<p begin="6714200000t" end="6721300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">咔咔</p>
<p begin="6730800000t" end="6754400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">你这是怎么了</p>
<p begin="6756900000t" end="6784300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">摆出一副鸽子中了竹枪子弹般的表情</p>
<p begin="6756900000t" end="6784300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">（注：鳩が豆鉄砲を食らったような顔、比喻惊慌失措）</p>
<p begin="6788700000t" end="6840100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">不  该说是吸血鬼中了银弹般的表情吗</p>
<p begin="6841300000t" end="6868300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">我开口说话有这么稀奇吗</p>
<p begin="6870000000t" end="6903900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">难道说你以为我已经不会说话了吗</p>
<p begin="6911400000t" end="6935700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">小忍  你…</p>
<p begin="6950500000t" end="6964500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">哼  我厌倦了</p>
<p begin="6967400000t" end="6988400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">我本来是会说话的</p>
<p begin="6990200000t" end="7006700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">这点你也很清楚吧</p>
<p begin="7008900000t" end="7038800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">真是的  怎么可能永远沉默下去呢</p>
<p begin="7041100000t" end="7071600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">还请你察觉到啊  我的主人</p>
<p begin="7127600000t" end="7136200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">谢谢你</p>
<p begin="7144000000t" end="7168500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">啊？你道什么谢啊</p>
<p begin="7170400000t" end="7184500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">啊  不…</p>
<p begin="7192100000t" end="7201400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">那是…</p>
<p begin="7206600000t" end="7217300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">你看这个</p>
<p begin="7219400000t" end="7242500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">是你帮我砍断这链子的吧</p>
<p begin="7244500000t" end="7265100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">是这样吗  咔咔</p>
<p begin="7266800000t" end="7282000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">我记不太清楚了</p>
<p begin="7284800000t" end="7319600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">但是罢了  你那手镯我也差不多看厌了</p>
<p begin="7323800000t" end="7330900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">来</p>
<p begin="7561700000t" end="7576700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">这点小事不用道谢</p>
<p begin="7580300000t" end="7604100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">我只是在做自己想做的事情而已</p>
<p begin="7614000000t" end="7640800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">从过去到现在  一直都是这样</p>
<p begin="7644500000t" end="7678600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">而这次只是偶然  真的只是偶然</p>
<p begin="7680900000t" end="7705000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">我和你的目的是一致的</p>
<p begin="7707300000t" end="7721100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">我的主人</p>
<p begin="7734600000t" end="7750000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">小忍  我说啊</p>
<p begin="7750800000t" end="7756700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">头发</p>
<p begin="7764500000t" end="7772500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">头发</p>
<p begin="7781300000t" end="7800300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">头…头发又怎么了</p>
<p begin="7801400000t" end="7819200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">帮我洗头发就好</p>
<p begin="7821100000t" end="7853500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">反正是闹着玩  我想试试那个什么叫洗发水的东西</p>
<p begin="7855500000t" end="7909500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">我暗中偷看你洗头的样子  一直都觉得很有趣</p>
<p begin="7911000000t" end="7930600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">我可以摸…吗？</p>
<p begin="7932200000t" end="7950700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">不摸的话怎么洗呢</p>
<p begin="7956000000t" end="7982500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">那就连护发也一起帮你做了吧</p>
<p begin="8036600000t" end="8042200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">我说啊</p>
<p begin="8043300000t" end="8050100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">停</p>
<p begin="8060600000t" end="8072900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">不要说话</p>
<p begin="8080500000t" end="8099400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">我不会原谅你</p>
<p begin="8101900000t" end="8125700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">你也不会原谅我吧</p>
<p begin="8132800000t" end="8141800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">这样就好</p>
<p begin="8146500000t" end="8168000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">我们不会原谅对方</p>
<p begin="8178900000t" end="8191900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">这样就行了吧</p>
<p begin="8197500000t" end="8225000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">我们不能把过去的事情付之一笑</p>
<p begin="8229200000t" end="8264900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">就算这样  也并不代表我们就不能亲近</p>
<p begin="8278400000t" end="8335400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">这就是我反复考虑了不知三个还是四个月所得出的结论</p>
<p begin="8347100000t" end="8373500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">如何呢  我的主人</p>
<p begin="8379800000t" end="8420700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">没想到你居然会考虑这种事情  真是出人意料</p>
<p begin="8423900000t" end="8452200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">你也考虑了很多事情对吧</p>
<p begin="8455500000t" end="8499900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">因为我最近都待在你的影子里  所以全都知道</p>
<p begin="8625400000t" end="8648700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">我也不会一直都生你的气</p>
<p begin="8650400000t" end="8677100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">我的气量没有那么小</p>
<p begin="8680200000t" end="8733700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">而且  看来不好好说出来的话你是不会领悟的</p>
<p begin="8735200000t" end="8741000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">嗯？</p>
<p begin="8742200000t" end="8762800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">我确实很喜欢吃波堤圈</p>
<p begin="8764300000t" end="8770100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">但</p>
<p begin="8773300000t" end="8800300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">我最喜欢吃的是黄金巧克力圈</p>
<p begin="8804000000t" end="8835800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">至少注意到这点  要买两个的话第二个就买那种</p>
<p begin="8861500000t" end="8873100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">明白了</p>
<p begin="8932900000t" end="8947300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">围栏火蜂</p>
<p begin="8949100000t" end="8967100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">属于大雀蜂类别的怪异</p>
<p begin="8968300000t" end="8985000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">这…难道是说…</p>
<p begin="8987400000t" end="9028000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">就是你那个巨大妹妹现在所惹上的怪异</p>
<p begin="9031300000t" end="9053900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">还没大到「巨大」那个份儿上</p>
<p begin="9057700000t" end="9088100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">我先说清楚  这当然不是来源于我的知识</p>
<p begin="9090500000t" end="9109900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">而是那个小子的知识</p>
<p begin="9112900000t" end="9136300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">你怎么可能理解我的心情</p>
<p begin="9144200000t" end="9177700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">那个轻薄至极的小子会旁若无人地</p>
<p begin="9179200000t" end="9231400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">将一些毫无用处的怪异故事滔滔不绝地讲上一整天</p>
<p begin="9233200000t" end="9270300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">而我却必须一言不发地听他说完时的心情</p>
<p begin="9285100000t" end="9294300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">这也太痛苦了</p>
<p begin="9301700000t" end="9323400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">这也是那些杂谈中的一个</p>
<p begin="9326200000t" end="9338200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">围栏火蜂</p>
<p begin="9340900000t" end="9346700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">记得好像是…</p>
<p begin="9358400000t" end="9384400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">室町时代前后发生的怪异吧</p>
<p begin="9386400000t" end="9426900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">简单说来就是原因不明的传染病</p>
<p begin="9429500000t" end="9476300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">这种传染病会引起让人无法动弹的高热</p>
<p begin="9479600000t" end="9502300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">最后甚至会致人死亡</p>
<p begin="9504200000t" end="9526100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">实际上也出现了数百名的牺牲者</p>
<p begin="9530400000t" end="9576900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">经过很长时间后  才有知名的阴阳师将其控制</p>
<p begin="9579000000t" end="9617800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">在什么什么书上好像就是这么写的</p>
<p begin="9619400000t" end="9642800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">换句话说  就是被无形的蜜蜂所刺</p>
<p begin="9644100000t" end="9672100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">身体好像被火焰所包围一样</p>
<p begin="9711200000t" end="9736700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">正因为火怜是那种性格</p>
<p begin="9740200000t" end="9753800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">故意装出一副坚强的样子</p>
<p begin="9757900000t" end="9780800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">我居然一时疏忽完全没有发觉</p>
<p begin="9786000000t" end="9819200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">她的身体似乎因此承受着巨大的负担</p>
<p begin="9827500000t" end="9843100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">高烧不止而浑身发热</p>
<p begin="9846800000t" end="9866900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">就好像正在燃烧一般</p>
<p begin="9873500000t" end="9898300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">就像被火焰所包围般灼热</p>
<p begin="9903500000t" end="9925000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">总之  是疾病</p>
<p begin="9958300000t" end="9986400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">真是的  怪不得羽川会帮她说话</p>
<p begin="9989800000t" end="10017500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">就算如此我还是认为她这是自作自受</p>
<p begin="10019100000t" end="10063600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">自作自受？你对家人还真是严格</p>
<p begin="10067600000t" end="10113600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">我一直在旁观  所以事到如今也不觉得有多吃惊</p>
<p begin="10115500000t" end="10153000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">不过虽然不像那位前任班长所说的那样</p>
<p begin="10155500000t" end="10169000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">我还真是感到有些意外</p>
<p begin="10170600000t" end="10185100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">前任班长？</p>
<p begin="10186000000t" end="10200400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">（那家伙现在也是班长啊）</p>
<p begin="10203000000t" end="10227400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">我也没打算这么严格对待她们</p>
<p begin="10234400000t" end="10260000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">不过  我家的妹妹不管怎么看来</p>
<p begin="10263100000t" end="10292800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">似乎是被贝木那家伙染上了怪异之毒了</p>
<p begin="10300000000t" end="10335990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">虽然我不知道这种事到底有没有可能发生</p>
<p begin="10337200000t" end="10363490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">很有可能啊  又不是做不到</p>
<p begin="10367200000t" end="10375300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">不过…</p>
<p begin="10387600000t" end="10417600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">如果那位傲娇小姑娘所说的话可信的话</p>
<p begin="10420600000t" end="10457500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">那个叫贝木的应该只是个冒牌的欺诈师才对</p>
<p begin="10420600000t" end="10457500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">伪物</p>
<p begin="10460000000t" end="10472600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">说的也是</p>
<p begin="10475300000t" end="10526600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">当然  又不是说冒牌货就不能使用真货的技能</p>
<p begin="10530700000t" end="10575600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">也可能正因为是冒牌货  才比真货显得更真</p>
<p begin="10577600000t" end="10588400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">真是至理名言</p>
<p begin="10592200000t" end="10622500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">的确  哪怕作为专家来说还是个半吊子</p>
<p begin="10625700000t" end="10652600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">作为欺诈师来说可能还真算的上一流</p>
<p begin="10653900000t" end="10675400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">半吊子的专家啊</p>
<p begin="10704800000t" end="10757900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">不过这样一来  似乎比独当一面的家伙更加麻烦</p>
<p begin="10760700000t" end="10786600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">用半生不熟的技巧来控制怪异</p>
<p begin="10790700000t" end="10813200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">就算在我看来也已经是超出常理了</p>
<p begin="10815700000t" end="10860000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">这哪是半吊子  简直都不算是人类了</p>
<p begin="10870600000t" end="10892200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">如果要给他的存在下一个定义的话</p>
<p begin="10895600000t" end="10929300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">那个家伙本身就算是一种怪异吧</p>
<p begin="10939100000t" end="10968900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">关于这些  我就去问问战场原好了</p>
<p begin="10972000000t" end="10989800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">不如说…也只能问她了</p>
<p begin="10994500000t" end="11008600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">目前所面临的问题是</p>
<p begin="11011300000t" end="11016300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">那家伙…</p>
<p begin="11030300000t" end="11048400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">在你面前也不用隐瞒吗</p>
<p begin="11053800000t" end="11062000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">火怜妹妹</p>
<p begin="11066400000t" end="11109600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">火怜妹妹的症状究竟该如何医治</p>
<p begin="11122600000t" end="11160700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">小忍  你能把火怜妹妹的病症吃掉吗</p>
<p begin="11184600000t" end="11196600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">很遗憾</p>
<p begin="11207300000t" end="11234600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">所谓的病症只是个结果</p>
<p begin="11237200000t" end="11257000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">就算我可以把蜜蜂美味地吃掉</p>
<p begin="11259300000t" end="11281600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">被蜜蜂所刺的结果却吃不掉</p>
<p begin="11283900000t" end="11309400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">也是啊  的确是这样</p>
<p begin="11311800000t" end="11322000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">那应该怎么做？</p>
<p begin="11325800000t" end="11362300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">忍野就没提过什么关于围栏火蜂的处置方法吗？</p>
<p begin="11374100000t" end="11412000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">是说还是没说呢…印象中他好像的确是说过</p>
<p begin="11414800000t" end="11443700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">不过也都是些啰啰唆唆的东西</p>
<p begin="11462700000t" end="11505800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">这么一想  还真是好久都没有泡过澡了  咔咔</p>
<p begin="11506900000t" end="11515800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">是吗</p>
<p begin="11516700000t" end="11522500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">嗯</p>
<p begin="11524900000t" end="11541700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">四百年没泡过了</p>
<p begin="11543700000t" end="11556900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">这规模还真是没法效仿啊</p>
<p begin="11590000000t" end="11606000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">你色眯眯地看什么呢</p>
<p begin="11611500000t" end="11638500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">居然对这种小孩子的裸体感到兴致勃勃</p>
<p begin="11641900000t" end="11661300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">你天生就是个变态吗</p>
<p begin="11662400000t" end="11685500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">不  我不是带着这种眼光来看的</p>
<p begin="11698200000t" end="11730600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">这样被你热切的目光所凝视</p>
<p begin="11733100000t" end="11769700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">我也会不由自主地想些有趣的事情</p>
<p begin="11770900000t" end="11775700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">啊？</p>
<p begin="11776500000t" end="11794200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">不不  都是些无聊的事情</p>
<p begin="11796100000t" end="11852300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">比如我现在发出一声能传遍整个房子的惨叫的话</p>
<p begin="11855500000t" end="11874000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">之后会怎么样呢</p>
<p begin="11883200000t" end="11890900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">诸如此类…</p>
<p begin="11895200000t" end="11909700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">也就仅此而已</p>
<p begin="11920300000t" end="11971500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">如果你愿意用大量甜甜圈来封住我的嘴的话</p>
<p begin="11975900000t" end="12015400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">我也是很乐意和你坐下来进行协商的</p>
<p begin="12024900000t" end="12038200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">有种你就试试</p>
<p begin="12041800000t" end="12059700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">我和你都是一根绳上的蚂蚱</p>
<p begin="12062400000t" end="12101600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">既然你跑不出我的影子  那你也别想全身而退</p>
<p begin="12104600000t" end="12136400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">最起码你再也吃不到Mister Donut的甜甜圈了</p>
<p begin="12137300000t" end="12160100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">咔咔  原来如此  你还有这一手</p>
<p begin="12162600000t" end="12193800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">看来你还是稍微成长了一些嘛  我的主人哟</p>
<p begin="12197500000t" end="12222500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">哥哥你要洗到什么时候</p>
<p begin="12224900000t" end="12247300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">接下来你不是要听我的故事吗</p>
<p begin="12266200000t" end="12274100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">那个…</p>
<p begin="12346000000t" end="12354100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">咦…</p>
<p begin="12409400000t" end="12416900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">咦？</p>
<p begin="12419600000t" end="12439800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">哥哥  刚才那个孩子呢</p>
<p begin="12441800000t" end="12451100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">刚才的孩子？</p>
<p begin="12460600000t" end="12473800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">你在说什么啊</p>
<p begin="12477100000t" end="12513400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">别在这紧要关头说这些不知所云的话啊  你个傻瓜</p>
<p begin="12525600000t" end="12543400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">是我看错了吗</p>
<p begin="12544400000t" end="12554800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">肯定是你看错了</p>
<p begin="12557300000t" end="12581000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">什么留着一头耀眼金发皮肤透明洁白…</p>
<p begin="12582800000t" end="12600600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398">操着一口古风还用高高在上的口气说话…</p>
<p begin="12602400000t" end="12620800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399">八岁左右胸平得像洗衣板一样的女孩儿</p>
<p begin="12623100000t" end="12634200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400">可从来没在这儿出现过</p>
<p begin="12644200000t" end="12651800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401">是吗</p>
<p begin="12683800000t" end="12703100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402">算了  我就不做追究了</p>
<p begin="12712500000t" end="12745300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403">哥哥  你洗得时间还真够长的</p>
<p begin="12747900000t" end="12761600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404">你到底打算洗到什么时候啊</p>
<p begin="12771300000t" end="12795200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405">马上就好  去客厅等我</p>
<p begin="12797200000t" end="12807000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406">好～</p>
<p begin="12809000000t" end="12824400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407">话说你倒是先敲门啊</p>
<p begin="12843400000t" end="12866000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408">之前你从来都没说过这种话吧</p>
<p begin="12868100000t" end="12883000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409">什么意思嘛  装出副成熟的样子</p>
<p begin="12886100000t" end="12926800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410">别因为最近健壮了点就给我得意忘形</p>
<p begin="12929600000t" end="12935800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411">哼</p>
<p begin="12984200000t" end="13012700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412">咔咔  我可真替你捏了一把汗啊</p>
<p begin="13015000000t" end="13028300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413">你妹妹的行为可真过激</p>
<p begin="13030600000t" end="13036900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle414">要你多嘴</p>
<p begin="13065900000t" end="13115400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle415">话说回来  有些事情那小子的确没有告诉过你</p>
<p begin="13118400000t" end="13148100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle416">大概他是有意在瞒着你吧</p>
<p begin="13153700000t" end="13185800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle417">你究竟什么时候会死呢？</p>
<p begin="13196000000t" end="13206700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle418">你这是什么意思？</p>
<p begin="13208300000t" end="13224500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle419">没什么  我只是想说…</p>
<p begin="13232500000t" end="13254900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle420">你几乎完全是个人类</p>
<p begin="13256800000t" end="13291100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle421">但同时还残留有少许吸血鬼的成分</p>
<p begin="13293200000t" end="13331500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle422">这样一来  你的寿命之类的又会有多长呢</p>
<p begin="13343800000t" end="13365100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle423">就算身体强度恢复了人类的水平</p>
<p begin="13367700000t" end="13392700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle424">说不定寿命还是和吸血鬼一样</p>
<p begin="13397200000t" end="13433200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle425">至少治愈能力好像还保留着</p>
<p begin="13439400000t" end="13451500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle426">说不定你和我一样</p>
<p begin="13454200000t" end="13492300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle427">别说四百年  就是五百年也能活下来</p>
<p begin="13545800000t" end="13555900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle428">恋人</p>
